            <div id="page-title">
    <h1>Indian IT Giant Strides Across Flat World to Fund Viterbi School Research</h1>
</div><!-- Ends: #PAGE-TITLE -->            
            <div class="contentDetail layout-1col-wide clearfix">
        
    <div class="col main">
        <div class="contentDetail">
	<div class="contentDetailNews">
	<h5>New Center for Research and Education in Advanced Software Technologies (CAST) at USC is company's first-ever outside of India</h5>
<div class="noprint" align="right">
 <table align="right" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0">
        <tr>
          <td valign="top">
<a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-via="USCViterbi">Tweet</a>
